158
00:10:35,466 --> 00:10:37,047
I'm sure she'll wake up soon.

159
00:10:38,096 --> 00:10:39,429
And the sooner, the better.

160
00:10:41,708 --> 00:10:42,464
Yeah.

161
00:10:48,686 --> 00:10:50,180
Hey, Kirito?

162
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:13,515
I wonder, did she log into S.A.O.
By herself or with her family?

163
00:11:14,245 --> 00:11:17,556
