284
00:16:26,827 --> 00:16:27,676
Okay.

285
00:16:28,057 --> 00:16:30,616
When she wakes up, we'll go to the town of beginnings.

286
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:33,112
That place is army territory.

287
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:36,998
