fully equipped, ready for anything.

288
00:16:37,554 --> 00:16:39,413
Yeah, we better be careful.

289
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,161
Mommy...

290
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,908
Daddy...

291
00:16:50,246 --> 00:16:52,238
