295
00:17:02,892 --> 00:17:04,918
Do any of these buildings look familiar?

296
00:17:05,792 --> 00:17:06,593
Uh...

297
00:17:07,792 --> 00:17:08,983
I don't know.

298
00:17:09,753 --> 00:17:13,161
Don't get down about the town of
beginnings is a really big place.

299
00:17:13,664 --> 00:17:14,658
