300
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:16,461
Should we start at the central market?

301
00:17:18,623 --> 00:17:19,655
Hey, Kirito?

302
00:17:20,242 --> 00:17:20,695
Yeah?

303
00:17:21,552 --> 00:17:24,701
