377
00:21:09,827 --> 00:21:10,454
Huh?

378
00:21:10,684 --> 00:21:12,065
Yui, what's the matter?

379
00:21:12,090 --> 00:21:12,933
Their hearts...

380
00:21:13,115 --> 00:21:13,711
Yui!

